The Sustainable Choice by @breez_lance ⁣
⁣
Check our new IGTV now, in which our Mango Girl talks about our main sustainable goals for the coming years! One of them is that by 2025, 100% of the cotton used in our garments will be sustainable, and this is great because by supporting its growth we are opting for natural fibre options with a reduced environmental impact, so we can be less and less dependent on non-renewable resources. ⁣
⁣
Brianna’s denim jumpsuit is made of 100% sustainable cotton + Eco-wash technique. ⁣
Jumpsuit: 17064055⁣
#MangoCommitted #MangoGirls

node.text:
The Sustainable Choice by @breez_lance ⁣
⁣
One of our main goals is that by 2025, 50% of our polyester will be recycled. With it we support a circular economy, in other words, extend the life of resources to the maximum, by reusing and recycling the waste that has the potential to become raw material again. If you want to know more, check out our new IGTV now! ⁣
⁣
Brianna’s bag is made of 100% recycled polyester. ⁣

#MangoCommitted
